{"tid":2082353,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美國眾議院議員: 呢啲青頭仔就係香港人","createTime":"2020-06-28T03:40:25.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-01T07:27:57.000Z","uid":83648,"like":1370,"dislike":17,"uniUserReply":110,"replies":[{"pid":"b478694788642b60ea0f24e5fe6b94129bbe831b","tid":2082353,"uid":83648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-28T03:40:25.000Z","msg":"佢首先問袁弓夷就咁睇覺得草硬啲定路硬啲<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/S8HEXEh.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FS8HEXEh.png&h=828b239b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n之後佢比喻草係代表自由民主而石屎路代表共產黨嘅壓迫，就咁睇就石屎梗係硬淨啲<br />\n<br />\n最後，佢比喻香港人係下圖嘅青頭仔，石屎係冚唔住啲青頭仔，最終香港人會破土而出<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wdnUMzm.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwdnUMzm.png&h=e466abca&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VUtEdet.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVUtEdet.png&h=85fe4822&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n願榮光歸香港<br />\n<br />\n豉油:<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/-JpLwEZiD38\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F-JpLwEZiD38&d=M%2BdtfvqsQfe3pFkx%2BxFNtPkum5iQZutveDYoRIbm5C0%3D&h=ba070980\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/-JpLwEZiD38</a>"},{"pid":"83511404fa04ee44c3e4a23168cf0e6f5bd7cdd5","tid":2082353,"uid":83648,"like":189,"dislike":5,"score":184,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-28T03:41:45.000Z","msg":"補返<br />\n佢叫Ted Yoho"},{"pid":"1bc71f104e3c5487f7c2470e4ecd8b952c2d2e02","tid":2082353,"uid":286897,"like":485,"dislike":3,"score":482,"citedBy":7,"replyTime":"2020-06-28T03:42:11.000Z","msg":"以為你話香港啲後生仔全部都係處男<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"681246dfd93b80d1ab8fbc09cb95c23f88e205fc","tid":2082353,"uid":265839,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-28T03:44:04.000Z","msg":"光復香港"},{"pid":"738a71d34a25cc5301b233a57923f5e8904aff