16:55:43.000Z","msg":"幽默嘅嘢 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b98ece7c918d7bd34e0324dfbcef2e4610435d1c","tid":2082353,"uid":211633,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-28T16:58:47.000Z","msg":"我地一定要破處<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a62207f43969039205f24bfedd527dfe0a6e5c8","tid":2082353,"uid":304769,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-28T17:01:11.000Z","msg":"七一大家要做場好戲比美國睇啊<br />\n<br />\n今年七一要加主題：<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n寧願最後不得善終<br />\n也不考慮含淚折衷<br />\n<br />\n我要美國制裁，無懼與支共同歸於盡，寧死捍衛自由民主</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n認同就拎張紙舉比美國睇，咪比條廢老Martin Lee騎劫我地，搞到美國以為我地驚攬炒而唔做野<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">黃世澤出左香港自治法篤灰指南，好有用，大家入去睇</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n\t<br />\n\t<a href=\"https://youtu.be/s6o2r5DkT-w\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fs6o2r5DkT-w&d=M%2BdtfvqsQfe3pFkx%2BxFNtPkum5iQZutveDYoRIbm5C0%3D&h=9d0bf0d4\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/s6o2r5DkT-w</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n借個位<br />\n正視聽：若抗爭方向不隨局勢改變，只會無謂地損兵折將<br />\n香港街頭抗爭目標，亦都係街頭抗爭最大效果；&ldquo;攬炒&rdquo;已經達到，今次搞蟈安法其實仲攬炒過上年出老解。<br />\n宜家<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">跟著落黎就係引導全球政府同議會（尤其美國）對付支那以及滅共</span></strong>，所以大家重點應該著眼帶出清晰民意授權比各國政府做野，畫面靚+全球廣泛報導（類似反蟈安法銅鑼灣自由行）係最理想，用選票帶出民意亦十分重要。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">大家要小心五毛、熱狗放負風向：美國唔會幫我地（舊年年尾）-》英國係廢國無用架（今年年頭）-》歐盟奶共唔會幫我地（宜家）</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n大家要記住，香港生路只有一條：救香港人+攬炒促進支爆+重建香港。<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">沒有支爆，香港獨立或者歸英等重建方案全部都係痴人說夢。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n未來幾個月至支共瓦解期間大家要做嘅事：1.<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">走資</span></strong>2.全球救生艇<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">救手足加有細路既黃絲家庭</span></strong>（細路是重點，香港未來棟樑，正如今時今日d前線義士，咪比佢地洗腦變小糞紅，否則香港係真正玩完）3.比足夠<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">民意授權，敦促美國以至各國凌遲式消除香港作為支那獲得外資渠道</span></strong>，包括但不限於：禁止美國個人或公司投資港股，暫停接受香港用美元結算等等4.最後就真係等<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>支那自己爆</strong></span>"},{"pid":"a4f6a8d5b343639326d911f50c17ee53eb1f1c7d","tid":2082353,"uid":249160,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-28T17:15:29.000Z","msg":"樓豬嘅演繹......<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"24f3311b363e6dd0218d4692ad513270f993a230","tid":2082353,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-28T17:23:59.000Z","msg":"推 7.1大遊行 tweet國際戰線 黃色經濟圈"},{"pid":"f396831bd68ac63e4adad67a1de4ef9eb85c4a08","tid":2082353,"uid":224479,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"1bc71f104e3c5487f7c2470e4ecd8b952c2d2e02","tid":2082353,"uid":286897,"like":485,"dislike":3,"score":482,"citedBy":7,"replyTime":"2020-06-28T03:42:11.000Z","msg":"以為你話香港啲後生仔全部都係處男<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-28T17:25:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frownsmile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e7385c86179c9d180bfa8d6a6fab28f5e066ea4","tid":2082353,"uid":360512,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-28T17:25:15.000Z","msg":"break through the ground that's why they will success and communist will fail."},{"pid":"156071e4c10f2c0bd9223c1bd91fba3cfee53578","tid":2082353,"uid":173207,"like":15,"dislike":2,"score":13,"quote":{"pid":"1bc71f104e3c5487f7c2470e4ecd8b952c2d2e02","tid":2082353,"uid":286897,"like":485,"dislike":3,"score":482,"citedBy":7,"replyTime":"2020-06-28T03:42:11.000Z","msg":"以為你話香港啲後生仔全部都係處男<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\"