: medium;\"><strong>[⇩ 港獨強心針 ⇩]</strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/pAcortX\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/pAcortX</a></span></div>"},{"pid":"9cb9ebe11bb64c3dab0bbe810c59b7c432cb5687","tid":2082353,"uid":104474,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-28T20:24:52.000Z","msg":"人之生也柔弱，其死也堅強。萬物草木之生也柔脆，其死也枯槁。故堅強者死之徒，柔弱者生之徒。是以兵強則不勝，木強則兵。強大處下，柔弱處上。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e77fc0249af86c30ee981ee83824f0323f4600bd","tid":2082353,"uid":31906,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-28T20:56:32.000Z","msg":"袁生最後好似喊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3acd058b7e0603c78f56e04c0720d24bba65f0f1","tid":2082353,"uid":296700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-28T21:00:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f6fbd4c718a4290da4cf868f05fd0f320a2a4e9","tid":2082353,"uid":296700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-28T21:00:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e264d5f7adeebd7e9551a6470d4c846834245302","tid":2082353,"uid":14503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-28T21:09:42.000Z","msg":"最後一幅圖係咪代表破處<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c4745be1a69283b7fde90c70e5eab7d1aecb9466","tid":2082353,"uid":55089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-28T21:33:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/